      "start_timestamp": "0:47",
      "end_timestamp": "0:48",
      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_16",
      "text": "In which I will ask you some medical history-related questions, and it will take 10 to 12 minutes, and this call will be recorded for company's audit and quality purposes.",
