      "start_timestamp": "2:00",
      "end_timestamp": "2:01",
      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_33",
      "text": "So sir, this call will be recorded for the company's audit and quality purposes, which will take 10 to 15 minutes, so shall we continue?",
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "start_timestamp": "2:02",
      "end_timestamp": "2:08",
      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_34",
      "text": "Sure, continue.",
      "speaker": "customer",
      "start_timestamp": "2:09",
      "end_timestamp": "2:10",
      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_35",
      "text": "Sir, I would like to inform you that during this call, any information you provide about your health and habits will become part of a legal contract between you and Tata AIA Insurance, and if any false or incorrect information is given, then the policy may be cancelled or the claim may be rejected later. So you are requested to give correct answers to all questions, okay?",
